.SH NAME
agx - Local multi-agent launcher: one relay profile for codex, claude, gemini, opencode


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBagx [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
agx is a single-user CLI that manages OpenAI-compatible relay profiles
(base_url + api_key) and launches each AI coding agent inside an isolated
managed context. Every mutation is captured and rollback-safe, so 'agx
backup' / 'agx restore' / 'agx doctor' can always recover from a half-
applied change.


